title: He's Living A Double Life
itunes:title: He's Living A Double Life
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I was a late bloomer and did not have a lot of dating experience until I was in my early twenties when I got braces and lost a little weight. Men loved it and would take advantage of me. I thought I had life figured out by the time I was twenty eight years old and I met the man I wanted to spend the rest of my life with..................
